Introducing our special dish Chicken Ghata, a true signature creation at Bhatti Chulo Lounge & Bar and one of the main reasons our guests keep coming back. This dish reflects our chef’s creativity, experience, and love for bold yet comforting flavors.

Chicken Ghata is prepared in a unique way where tender chicken keema is carefully filled inside chicken wings so you can enjoy the taste without worrying about bones getting in the way. Every bite is smooth, juicy, and full of flavor, making it both satisfying and easy to eat. The chicken is perfectly seasoned, cooked to the right texture, and served hot to bring out its rich aroma and taste.

This specialty dish has quickly become a favorite among guests who visit us as a family, with friends, or for a relaxed meal. Many of our customers who search for the best restaurant in Kathmandu love Chicken Ghata for its originality and balance of taste. It is also a great choice for those exploring a restaurant near Baneshwor that offers something different from the usual menu.

At Bhatti Chulo, we focus on quality, hygiene, and comfort, which is why our kitchen puts special care into every serving. Whether you are visiting as a couple, with family, or simply looking for a calm bar in Kathmandu with great food, Chicken Ghata is a must-try. Come and experience one of our proudest creations, made to be enjoyed slowly and remembered long after the last bite.
